    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Costs Breakdown</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Austria's investor visa involves various setup and ongoing costs. The main financial requirements are the €50,000+ investment (for Self-Employed Key Worker category) plus business establishment and living costs.
    </p>

    <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">Total Cost Estimates by Scenario</h3>

