        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">US Tech Founder, SaaS Start-up in Vienna</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">33 years old, accepted into Vienna's tech accelerator program. Building B2B software with €100K seed funding from Austrian angel investors.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">Approved in 8 weeks via Start-up Founder Visa. Accelerator support streamlined the application. Formed GmbH with €10,000 privileged capital. Using Allianz Care for initial coverage (€180/month), will switch to SVS + supplement once revenue starts. Now employing 2 developers, expanding into DACH market.</p>
