      <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">German Management Consultant, Vienna Office</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">42 years old, 15 years consulting experience. Opening Vienna branch to serve Central/Eastern European clients. €80,000 investment in office and operations.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">Approved in 6 weeks as Self-Employed Key Worker. German language and existing client relationships strengthened application. WKO assessment highlighted regional expertise gap. Using Austrian private insurance (UNIQA) from day one (€250/month). Business profitable within 6 months.</p>
