        <p class="text-amber-700 font-medium">Approved after 10 weeks with additional documentation. WKO requested detailed market analysis and supplier contracts—provided letters of intent from UK producers and Austrian distributors. Family covered under SVS once business launched. Children enrolled in Austrian schools. Integration going well with German lessons.</p>
