        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">Application rejected. WKO couldn't identify economic benefit—no clear business model, target market, or job creation plan. Advised to develop concrete business concept with market research. Reapplied 6 months later with specific e-commerce niche, supplier agreements, and marketing plan. Second application approved. Lesson: Austrian authorities expect detailed, realistic business plans.</p>
